{"tid":689110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【科技●國際專欄】facebook佈局「偷」你電話簿 教你一招可以刪除","createTime":"2018-06-03T23:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T06:55:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d2fb78a433a5b5853bbdf7370f791d54c502c79","tid":689110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T23:36:38.000Z","msg":"誰偷走了我的電話簿？ 撰文︰盤古目<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180603/large/1528014977_c993.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180603%2Flarge%2F1528014977_c993.jpg&h=a88d81ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個人資料是21世紀的金鑛，各家各戶網絡公司都扭盡六壬從用家身上攞料，攞得料多就生米變熟飯，你以後係我嘅人，任我魚肉。以至被圈養的我們亦落落大方；「我都冇秘密嘅，咪由得佢攞囉。」說的人落落大方，卻不見得會好順攤咁俾老婆睇佢相簿、電話簿或聊天對話。<br />\n早前的Facebook私隱醜聞發生時香港人都似隔岸觀火，可能認為Facebook有的個人資料多極有限，頂多是我like邊個、上載咗啲相之類，但似乎不知Facebook這十幾年間，尤其透過手機應用，包括Facebook app、Facebook Messenger，不但管有你主動分享的文字、照片、位置等等作材料，好多用家「唔覺唔覺」啟動Facebook同步功能，在我們安裝時那一窩蜂的設定中，經已佈局將我們電話中的電話簿甚至通話紀錄同步備份，電話簿、通話紀錄甚至SMS內容經已存到Facebook保管，你的一言一行、生活圈子，加上Facebook安插在其他網站上的like button，都是監察你日常喜好的探子，基本上已離不開朱克伯格手指罅。<br />\n因應近日有關個人資料的要求，Facebook現提供下載個人資料途徑，大家可用電腦上 Facebook設定頁（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/settings）下載，翻睇自己過往十多年來意想不到咁詳細的歷史，真係個心都離一離。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsettings%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%BF%BB%E7%9D%87%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%80%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%84%8F%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%92%81%E8%A9%B3%E7%B4%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%EF%BC%8C%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%80%8B%E5%BF%83%E9%83%BD%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%80%E9%9B%A2%E3%80%82&d=vzNaOYh9vM3wKlqSaL%2BMthv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9b6fbc14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/settings）下載，翻睇自己過往十多年來意想不到咁詳細的歷史，真係個心都離一離。</a><br />\n有人見到可能晴天霹靂，但話唔埋有人發現之前壞電話、唔見電話時冇咗的電話資料竟然冰封於此，反而感激Facebook，以身相許。<br />\n大家不妨到以下兩個Facebook連結望望，睇吓Facebook有冇keep到你的電話簿及通話紀錄，之後亦可到呢兩個app的設定中關閉通訊錄同步功能。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180604/58271447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180604%2F58271447&d=vzNaOYh9vM3wKlqSaL%2BMthv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=28645cee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180604%2F58271447&h=977b2337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180604/58271447</a>"},{"pid":"39039c9fc268126835f5a58aabb3d82d194906e5","tid":689110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a267e4fc27f7717182f6f797fb5e1a9e93f5d92","tid":689110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58269a473839a617877cd3dd787667f4d121e399","tid":689110,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"delete facebook app 好過啦"},{"pid":"535c76431eadbed5f818479febebf5cc23354a49","tid":689110,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"D真樣都可以upload上去，怕咩失電話薄"}]}